	(text "Power can come from three AA batteries or one Li-on 18650 cell.\n* Three alkaline AA batteries have a nominal voltage of 4.5V (max 4.8V).\n* Three lithium AA batteries (primary, not rechargeable) have a new voltage of 5.4V\n* 18650 cell has nominal voltage of 4.2 fully charged, 3.7V nominal.\n* All cells has a minimum voltage of 3.0V"
